      "id": "n_wdt_dml_wdt_rationale_216",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "Control register INTEN enables the watchdog and RESEN enables reset on a second timeout. Toggling INTEN reloads or freezes the counter and (re)schedules the countdown; STEP_VALUE selects the _27ac1234.md",
